drbd
	drbd sys-v type init script
drbd.gentoo
	gentoo specific variation of the same
drbddisk
	resource script for heartbaet (haresources style)
block-drbd
	xen "drbd" vbd type implementation
outdate-peer.sh
	example implementation of the outdate-peer mechanism using ssh
drbd.conf
	commented example configuration
drbd-overview.pl
	consolidates /proc/drbd, /etc/drbd.conf, xm list, lvs, df
pretty-proc-drbd.sh
	example how to pretty-print (optionally with color) /proc/drbd

